{"tid":500223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和電承認有員工被解僱[IT again]","createTime":"2017-12-15T14:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T15:08:50.000Z","uid":84436,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dbe9a4ef2f427c276ee61efbe81dd017d6d19318","tid":500223,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T14:39:31.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20171215/20245536\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171215%2F20245536&d=%2FRaH1x5qWITByysv8wuJn6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=567c25e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171215%2F20245536&h=7ba3d4e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20171215/20245536</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n【本報訊】臨近年尾，和記電訊（215）爆出裁員疑雲。有員工指要「估估吓」自己會否收大信封。有和電員工向《蘋果》報料指，昨早開始，和電青衣總部出現裁員，數十名IT員工。和電方面雖承認昨日確有員工被解僱，但指涉及幾個人，強調無裁員計劃。<br />\n稱已提供優厚補償<br />\n該名和電員工表示，今次被裁的人員包括一些坐房的中層，甚至「成條team剷起」，收到裁員通知後需即時離職。他續指，自己雖未被裁，但擔心隨時會收到解僱通知，又指不少同事都有家庭，年尾被裁對生活造成很大壓力。<br />\n和電回覆，公司並無裁員計劃，是次已為數位離職員工提供較勞工法例優厚的離職補償或轉職安排。和電表示，由於處身競爭激烈的市場環境，不得不時常作內部檢討，在必要時調配人力資源，以提升效率及競爭力。<br />\n自香港寬頻（1310）去年殺入流動通訊市場後，電訊商間不時爆發減價戰，影響和電收入及盈利。去年和電全年盈利跌23.4%%，至7.01億元；今年業績亦同樣受壓，上半年少賺10%至3.24億元。"},{"pid":"7a25f1b00d887373b91a744f30568b863ed35a3d","tid":500223,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T14:39:53.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"e551dd03a037cc6af5a43db8aa6a3accb90b1852","tid":500223,"uid":51134,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T14:40:25.000Z","msg":"痴撚線公司"},{"pid":"34f0882a4d4c77a4a5d7b060125195e89f14b3c7","tid":500223,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T14:40:59.000Z","msg":"HK No IT"},{"pid":"bad57dd4f516953c9f02645ff3df153540067466","tid":500223,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T14:58:06.000Z","msg":"陸續有黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0250a9da3add229f8f6f6ef22334a1dd1a5826a5","tid":500223,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T14:58:34.000Z","msg":"it狗近況幸福嗎"},{"pid":"4107d9626e74f44cabd2e1bdf0137cdda70e996a","tid":500223,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T15:01:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>陸續有黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78af4808fde545700be4791caa4162cf486762aa","tid":500223,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T09:53:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b5a7555e9459c59942d1dbf18888c1a5eb4c6d","tid":500223,"uid":71676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T09:55:05.000Z","msg":"IT狗又可以開心過年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef13f65842066839a32b000a2588bd19e640d80","tid":500223,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T14:41:42.000Z","msg":"年尾冰冷無情雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d695c90a5867e061f13f8224fca840e26a69bdd","tid":500223,"uid":158504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T15:08:50.000Z","msg":"hknoit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}